<TITLE>2024 UW Brain Awareness Week Speakers Bureau</TITLE>
</HEAD><body>

<center><h2>2024 University of Washington Brain Awareness Week Speakers 
Bureau</h2></center>
 
<center><table>
<tr>

<td><p>Neuroscientists at the University of Washington (UW) will speak 
about the exciting field of brain research. Teachers interested in 
having a neuroscientist visit (virtually or in-person) can request a 
speaker.</p>

<p>If you are interested in having a neuroscientist speak with your students, please complete <a href="https://forms.gle/ngMoLyUjeoc5ir43A">this form.</a></p>


</td>

<td><img src="baw/bawnewi.gif" width="128" height="124" alt="baw logo" /></td></tr>
</table></center>

